74
00:04:43,500 --> 00:04:46,853
We subtract these damaged tins from the total: five thousand

75
00:04:46,953 --> 00:04:50,363
six hundred and forty minus two hundred and eighty-two leaves

76
00:04:50,463 --> 00:04:54,162
